awscc_resourceexplorer2_view (Data Source)

Data Source schema for AWS::ResourceExplorer2::View

Schema

Read-Only

  • included_properties (Attributes List) (see below for nested schema)

  • tags (Map of String)
  • view_arn (String)
  • view_name (String)
